# {{project_name}}

A fungible token contract implementing the standard Soroban token interface
(`soroban_sdk::token::TokenInterface`, SEP-41) plus an admin-gated `mint`,
generated by [soroban-forge](https://github.com/soroban-forge-labs/soroban-forge)
from the `token` template.

## Features

- `transfer`, `transfer_from`, `approve`/`allowance` (with expiration ledger),
  `burn`, `burn_from`, `balance`, `decimals`, `name`, `symbol`
- Admin-only `mint`, set at deploy time via the constructor
- Storage TTL management following the official token example

## Develop

```sh
cargo test
stellar contract build
```

## Deploy to testnet

The constructor takes `admin`, `decimals`, `name`, `symbol`:

```sh
stellar contract deploy \
  --wasm target/wasm32v1-none/release/{{crate_name}}.wasm \
  --source-account <your-identity> \
  --network testnet \
  -- --admin <ADMIN_ADDRESS> --decimals 7 --name "My Token" --symbol MYT
```
